node.text:
It’s so crazy it’s been 2 years since she came into my life! Time really does fly with these angels!
•
She is the sassiest, funniest, prettiest girl. Just like her momma!
•
We made cupcakes and dad forgot to get candles. So we improvised with moms smell good candle!
•
There is nothing I love more than being a Dad and this little girl makes that the best job in the world!
•
Happy Birthday baby!
@the_diesel_des @saylor_fe

node.text:
On their last flight they bring out the water cannons and spray the plane with awesome arches of water. Well, this COVID stuff has changed that tradition, but we weren’t about to let my old man retire without giving him the proper sendoff! So we surprised him with a water cannon tradition of our own!
•
This man taught me everything about hard honest work and to take pride in what you do. He taught me in his actions as he worked himself day in and day out to provide an amazing life for our family. When he wasn’t flying in the AirForce or for Delta he was working hard on our house and yard and other projects. The man doesn’t know how to sit still! Haha, that’s probably where I get it from!
•
I’m extremely thankful for such an amazing father and example in my life who has taught me to work hard to provide for those you love. I’m excited to see the amazing things he does now during retirement!!! Haha I’m sure he is already building a plane or some sort of flying machine to get back into the sky!
•
Love you Dad

node.title: There is an awesome tradition when pilots retire called the water salute.

node.text:
Once upon a time a group of warriors found themselves in an epic battle with a slithering demon who was trying to stop them from freeing the water to save a village of cattle. Well, the cliff notes version of the story is the warriors were victorious in their battle, they saved the cows, and one hero paid respect to the Gods and their worthy opponent by swallowing it’s still beating heart!
•
 Legend has it that he is now half man half rattlesnake!
•
Legend also says that today is his birthday!!! Hit up ol @hans_smco and tell him what nickname he earned from this!
•
We think rattler or snake heart, but we are open to other suggestions! Haha
•
Happy birthday buddy!! You are the most driven, hardest working, fun loving dude around and still find a way to be an incredible dad! I look up to you brother! Hope you have the best birthday EVER!!!
